===Noun===
'''tail'''

#The [[caudal]] [[appendage]] of an [[animal]] that is attached to its [[posterior]] and near the [[anus]].
#The [[visible]] [[stream]] of [[dust]] and [[gas]]es blown from a [[comet]] by the [[solar wind]].
#One who [[surreptitious]]ly [[follow]]s another.
#{{Cricket}} The last four or five [[batsman|batsmen]] in the [[batting order]], usually [[specialist]] [[bowlers]].

